# CentOS Stream 9 Installation in VirtualBox

This guide documents how I installed CentOS Stream 9 in VirtualBox as part of my IT learning journey.

## ISO Used
- File: CentOS-Stream-9-latest-x86_64-dvd1.iso
- Size: ~7.2 GB (full DVD ISO)

## VirtualBox Settings
- OS Type: Linux
- Version: Red Hat (64-bit)
- Memory: 2048 MB (2 GB)
- Disk: 20 GB
- EFI: Enabled
- Video Memory: 64 MB
- Mounted ISO on Controller: IDE

## Steps
1. Boot VM and select “Install CentOS Stream 9”
2. Skip media check
3. Select language and region
4. Set up:
   - Installation destination
   - Network & hostname
   - Root password and user creation
5. Begin installation and reboot

